{
  "info": {
    "name": "Smart Delivery - Package Service",
    "description": "# Package Service\n\nManages customer packages, statuses, and delivery progress for the Smart Delivery System.\n\n## Features\n- Create, Read, Update, Delete packages\n- Track packages by tracking number\n- Update delivery status\n- Assign packages to routes\n- Record delivery confirmation\n\n## Package Statuses\n| Status | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `pending` | Package created, awaiting pickup |\n| `picked-up` | Package picked up from sender |\n| `in-transit` | Package in transit |\n| `out-for-delivery` | Package out for final delivery |\n| `delivered` | Package delivered successfully |\n| `failed` | Delivery attempt failed |\n| `returned` | Package returned to sender |\n\n## Priority Levels\n- `low` - Standard delivery (3-5 days)\n- `medium` - Express delivery (1-2 days)\n- `high` - Priority delivery (same day)\n\n## Base URL\n- Direct: `http://localhost:3003`\n- Via Gateway: `http://localhost:3000/api/packages`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
